16:24.790 --> 16:26.630
Good morning, Sensei.

16:26.630 --> 16:27.960
Hello, Sou-chan.

16:27.960 --> 16:29.250
How are you?

16:34.630 --> 16:36.010
Sousuke!

16:36.010 --> 16:36.930
