17:37.700 --> 17:40.070
It's not a goldfish. It's Ponyo.

17:40.070 --> 17:42.370
Ponyo? I want to see!

17:42.750 --> 17:44.830
Promise not to tell?

17:44.830 --> 17:46.120
I promise.

17:48.170 --> 17:50.130
Isn't she cute?

17:56.380 --> 18:00.300
It looks weird and fat. My goldfish is much cuter.

18:22.700 --> 18:27.040
It's Kumiko-chan's fault. She was mean to you.

18:30.750 --> 18:32.840
I'll give you some more water.

18:55.150 --> 18:56.110
Ponyo!

19:03.240 --> 19:04.120
You scared me.

19:09.460 --> 19:15.130
Why, how odd. That was Sousuke-chan's voice.

19:16.090 --> 19:20.340
