30:45.190 --> 30:47.990
Ponyo loves Sousuke.

30:47.990 --> 30:50.990
I want to be human!

30:51.490 --> 30:52.950
Human?

30:52.950 --> 30:55.830
How could you love such disgusting creatures?

30:56.620 --> 30:59.410
They rob the sea of life.

31:00.170 --> 31:02.830
I was human myself... once.

31:03.290 --> 31:05.990
I finally escaped that awful heritage...

31:05.990 --> 31:08.170
I want hands!

31:08.720 --> 31:11.180
I don't like this!

31:12.010 --> 31:15.060
I want legs like Sousuke!

31:15.060 --> 31:16.640
Of all the nonsense!

31:35.950 --> 31:39.410
Look at me! Hands and feet!

31:40.000 --> 31:40.850
Look at me!

31:40.850 --> 31:44.750
