32:21.500 --> 32:22.710
Let me out!

32:22.710 --> 32:26.130
Be still, you evil blood.

32:26.130 --> 32:28.960
Revert, revert!

32:38.220 --> 32:42.020
Just like her mother... So strong.

32:47.230 --> 32:50.440
She should remain innocent and pure forever.

33:11.420 --> 33:14.510
I can't hold her for long.

33:14.510 --> 33:17.050
I need her mother's help.

33:26.350 --> 33:29.150
