34:43.719 --> 34:45.270
Superb!

34:45.270 --> 34:49.810
I feel the ocean's power in my very DNA.

34:50.440 --> 34:54.860
When this well is full, the Era of the Ocean will begin.

34:54.860 --> 34:58.110
An explosion of life to match the Cambrian Era!

34:58.110 --> 35:00.820
This revolting era of Man will be over.

35:05.870 --> 35:07.500
Better fix this door.

36:31.620 --> 36:33.080
Teeth!

36:41.090 --> 36:43.340
